getPSDELogicNodes.name: 获取用例步骤
getPSDELogicNodes.sql: select concat('[', GROUP_CONCAT(t1.casestep),']') as casestep from (SELECT JSON_OBJECT('case', t1.`CASE`,'desc', t1.`DESC`,'expect', t1.`EXPECT`,'id', t1.`ID`,'parent', t1.`PARENT`,'type', t1.`TYPE`,'version', t1.`VERSION`) as casestep,t1.`case`,t1.version  FROM `zt_casestep` t1) t1 where t1.`case` = ? and t1.version =? GROUP BY t1.`case`,t1.version
